{"tid":2327454,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"飲醉左其實意識係咪仲清醒？亂表白/攬人果d係咪扮醉？","createTime":"2020-12-16T05:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-19T23:16:56.000Z","uid":309049,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"717e07424954da0fed798ffb028b3e5420a66df2","tid":2327454,"uid":309049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"我自己經驗係飲幾多個腦都好清醒，知道自己做緊咩，只係身體控制唔到，冇晒力。<br />\n再醉d就想訓覺，不省人事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以果d以飲醉為名做既事，例如表白，錫人，打人，跳舞，然後第二日話咩都唔記得，其實係咪扮醉？"},{"pid":"b0df1cf2f7843dd24a5bbf0c6cd47fea6b0cca58","tid":2327454,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:28:44.000Z","msg":"咁係你未真正醉過<br />\n<br />\n飲幾多都清醒？ 你飲啤酒想醉？"},{"pid":"ea11fe5604bbc6651c6798f7164516acf22c6b71","tid":2327454,"uid":177089,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:30:21.000Z","msg":"醉酒係會失去自制力"},{"pid":"487392ad8766a897da87a3a27486a56a5c8eb264","tid":2327454,"uid":8113,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"酒醉三分醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497fed74813a194de343a78a53c5724119c15df3","tid":2327454,"uid":109864,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T10:20:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1e9ecd9ca2375e945a18b88ca9c03ee92d7d25","tid":2327454,"uid":302895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T23:16:56.000Z","msg":"係唔夠醉<br />\n試過有次真係醉到斷片<br />\n醉到我個frd同我講反我做左咩我都o撚左嘴<br />\n<br />\n但其實好少會醉到咁<br />\n同埋斷片之後一定會訓<br />\n<br />\n如果佢到走個刻 都係無訓過 咁佢一定唔係無意識"}]}